EntityClassTranslator
public class ClassTranslator<T>
extends MapNodeTranslator<T>

Translator which knows what to do with a whole class. This is used by the EmbedClassTranslatorFactory and also subclassed to produce a RootClassTranslator, which is managed specially.

Author:
Jeff Schnitzer
